&kp TAB         &kp LEFT_ARROW      &kp DOWN_ARROW  &kp RIGHT_ARROW      &kp END  &trans      &kp PAGE_UP    &kp HOME  &kp LEFT         &kp DOWN  &kp RIGHT    &kp END
&kp LEFT_SHIFT  &kp LG(LEFT_ARROW)  &kp LG(TAB)     &kp LG(RIGHT_ARROW)  &trans   &trans      &kp PAGE_DOWN  &trans    &none            &trans    &none        &caps_word
&trans          &trans              &trans          &trans               &trans   &trans      &trans         &trans                                            &trans
